                            <comment id="14449679" author="kbarrett" created="Mon, 27 Sep 2021 14:55:36 -0700"  >The use of facilities in &amp;lt;type_traits&amp;gt; is already permitted.  This includes std::alignment_of&amp;lt;&amp;gt;, which is just a metafunction that returns the corresponding alignof value.  The metafunction predates the operator in the development of the standard; the operator provides less verbose syntax.&lt;br/&gt;
